						<summary>

						<p>Records a sale of land to the <hi rend="italic">kaṉmis</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Nambirāṭṭiyār Lōkamahādēviyār</hi> free of all taxes for five years from the year of assignment and thereafter for payment of a stipulated quantity of paddy into the temple treasury. The sale was made at the instance of <hi rend="bold">Nārāyaṇabhaṭṭar,</hi> the <hi rend="italic">Śrīkāryam</hi> officer.</p>						

						</summary>
